snippet.title: Disney's Master Mouse Show Time Quiz PC Gameplay
snippet.description: Disney's Master Mouse Show Time Quiz (known as Dsney's Trivia Challenge in USA) is a quiz game released by Disney Interactive and developed by Imagine Engine in 2001. This game is to mark 100 years of Disney.
